d 'SJ1': module providing Enhanced Stata Journal Navigator 
d
d  sj1 provides enhanced navigation for the Stata Journal,
d simplifying access to SJ content.   sj1 is an enhanced version of
d official commands with these benefits:      • Automatically
d formats output with journal metadata and statistics	   •
d Supports batch display of all issues in a volume	•
d Provides clickable PDF links for one-click paper access      •
d Displays DOI identifiers for academic citation 
d
d KW: Stata Journal
d
d Requires: Stata version 
d
d Distribution-Date: 20250603
d
d Author: Wang Qiang, Xi'an Jiaotong University
d Support: email  740130359@@qq.com
d
